data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Short Sale. Welcome to your new oasis just 5.2 miles from beautiful Siesta Key Beach!! Step inside and be greeted by a bright and airy open floor plan. This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath is a rare opportunity to own a large pool home without the HOA or CDD fees. Near shopping and some of the most beautiful beaches in the world. You can live your dream of owning a pool home in paradise or turn this amazing investment home into an air B&B or VRBO .Average rental on a home of this size with game room, bar, and pool  is over $6000 per month. Come by and see this beauty it won't be on the market for long!
